    <!-- Privacy Notice -->
    <string name="privacy_title">Privacy Notice</string>
    <string name="privacy_body">AutoExpense reads your SMS messages to automatically detect UPI and bank transactions. Optionally, you can enable reading payment-related text from notifications in Settings (Android notification listener); that stays on your device only.\n\n🔒 Your data is 100% private:\n• All data is stored locally on your device\n• No SMS or notification text is uploaded to any server\n• No personal information is shared with third parties\n• You can delete all data at any time from Settings\n\nThis app uses READ_SMS and RECEIVE_SMS solely to detect payment alerts. You can disable SMS capture or notification capture independently in Settings.\n\nBy tapping "Accept &amp; Continue", you agree to grant these permissions for the purpose described above.</string>
